title: The REAL Garden of Eden has been Found-Stan Deyo-mp4
description:
This  radio broadcast interview took place on The Haggman and Haggman Report.An internet Christian news show with guest speaker " The real life Indiana Jones", Stan Deyo.It aired on 8-6-2014 . The lecture/interview begins about the 50 minute mark,so feel free to skip ahead.In this broadcast, Stan tells HOW he found the Garden of Eden,and WHERE it is today.Towards the end of the show,he begins to tell us his thoughts on the anti-Christ and the false prophet.Where they are today and even who he Thinks fits the profile. He will even go into the topic of King Solomans gold mines,and where they were/are. Website links and information are provide in the broadcast.

 Although Mr. Deyo proposes many unconventional theories,there are a large number of other archaeologist,and anthropologist who agree with him about the smaller Earth.
